    <briefdescription>
<para>USB device controller event. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Common structure for all events that originate from the UDC driver and are passed to higher layer using message queue and a callback (udc_event_cb_t) provided by higher layer during controller initialization (udc_init). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
